{"tid":1609891,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論]蟲系魔法師的攻擊目標","createTime":"2019-10-01T15:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T17:02:06.000Z","uid":169254,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1e15c98eb341f05a6520ea1d4a230eac5d89450d","tid":1609891,"uid":169254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:46:31.000Z","msg":"小弟最近玩緊隻好多人玩嘅RTS<br />\n有面有得用唔同兵種通關<br />\n近排patch完出咗隻蟲魔法師<br />\n見到好多人討論過水/火魔法師 但係就冇見過蟲系魔法師嘅攻略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以想喺度傾下點樣將佢擺入去宜家個meta度<br />\n喺度拋磚引玉先<br />\n今日見到有人放咗招技落個皇家辦事處度<br />\n雖然做法好有新意<br />\n但係仲有改善空間<br />\n下次放嘅話<br />\n會唔會有啲更加好嘅地方去放<br />\n例如係支持紅色魔王嘅咩心 乜嘢家等等嘅補給站<br />\n扣血可能會扣得多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 純遊戲攻略討論"},{"pid":"2c9c38d3d44021ab33a468ab969e0c910e4edd97","tid":1609891,"uid":169254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:46:53.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 (1/10)"},{"pid":"6bfa04c9582437863459613be6f48baf130b8a24","tid":1609891,"uid":169254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:47:04.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 (2/10)"},{"pid":"8c3367595ffbf32888ae275fd643f35875f5abfb","tid":1609891,"uid":9457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:47:20.000Z","msg":"狹窄環境<br />\n雞蛋附魔"},{"pid":"4d0d8ce637c1864454fa25ff83058c668634d99c","tid":1609891,"uid":169254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:48:10.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 (3/10)"},{"pid":"8837e637efd352d35f38c2844157c3a9127da7e8","tid":1609891,"uid":169254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:48:30.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 (4/10)"},{"pid":"f329a52a1f454474de10ca0c4104630b701e0345","tid":160